Skills.Name: Want a Cookie?
Skills.Description:
Recovers HP of single ally with lowest HP by <color=red>{0}%</color> of
ATK.

Skills.Name: Wrapped in Happiness
Skills.Description:
Raises DEF of single ally with highest DEF by <color=red>{0}%</color> for
10s. Further recovers HP by {1}% of ATK if Blue Elemental.
Skills.ShortDescription:
Raises DEF of single ally,
recovers HP if Blue Elemental

Skills.Name: Parade Time
Skills.Description: Recovers HP of all allies by <color=red>{0}%</color> of ATK. Further raises ATK by <color=red>{1}%</color> for 10s if Blue Elemental.
Skills.ShortDescription: Recovers HP of all allies, raises ATK if Blue Elemental

Skills.Name: Strike Combo
Skills.Description: Recovers HP of all allies by <color=red>5.00%-50.00%</color> according to Combo Bonus. Inflicts 100.00% DMG.
Skills.ShortDescription:
Recovers HP of all allies,
inflicts DMG on single enemy
